Welcome, Attorney Segal. We are going to have kind of four standard questions. Counselor Callahan is going to run through them. And then if counselors have follow-up questions, we will ask you some follow-up questions. Counselor Callahan. Thank you. First of all, thank you for being here.

52
00:21:17,013 --> 00:21:33,972
