58
00:23:22,478 --> 00:23:32,975
Thank you. Our second question, what do you think are the most pressing issues to be addressed by the new city clerk and how would you address them?

59
00:23:33,110 --> 00:24:03,029
I think an immediate priority is we know that there is some backlog that has accumulated on codifying city ordinances in part just due to gaps in staffing. So I think that that's a high priority to bring that back up to date and also look at perhaps further measures that we can take to ensure that there is less of a possibility of establishing a backlog in the future.

60
00:24:03,029 --> 00:24:18,858
