00:30:56,737 --> 00:31:23,720
Thank you, Laurel. Thank you, Attorney Segal. At this point, you know, we will go into kind of our deliberations. Procedurally, we would make a motion after our discussions to recommend a candidate, then engage in an offer process and negotiation. When that's completed, we would then have

