00:33:31,936 --> 00:34:00,488
narrowed down the candidates, and now we have this process here. So, both candidates are qualified and intelligent, and they have experience in Medford, and it's so hard to talk about personnel stuff publicly, but I would love for us to get the ball rolling, and since I have talked about

